&lt;p&gt;We are currently recruiting a Registered Nurse to ensure that an individual programme of care is planned, implemented and evaluated for each patient within their own sphere of responsibility. They will work as part of the multidisciplinary team ensuring the delivery of a high standard of care to the patients. and to act as a positive role model at all times&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will be a 1st or 2nd level registered nurse (RGN) with experience of working in a multi-disciplinary environment and knowledge of appropriate clinical treatment options for patients.&lt;/p&gt;
